pageContext.claim: “The great USMCA Trade Deal (Mexico & Canada) has been sitting on Nancy Pelosi’s desk for 8 months, she doesn't even know what it says, & today, after passing by a wide margin in the House, Pelosi tried to take credit for it. Labor will vote for Trump. Trade deal is great for USA!”
pageContext.analysis: The trade deal was not "sitting" on Pelosi's desk for eight months, as the administration had not sent implementing legislation while it negotiated with House Democrats on ways to makes changes that would win enough votes for passage.
